OL,3,COvercrowded and understaffed -
OL,4,CScottish prisons pushed to "crisis
OL,5,Cpoint"
OL,7,FIt states that a "toxic combination"
OL,8,Fof overcrowding and understaffing is
OL,9,Fputting extreme pressure on workers,
OL,10,Fand it is urging the Scottish
OL,11,FGovernment to act to reduce the
OL,12,Fpressure.
OL,14,FStatistics released by the Scottish
OL,15,FPrison Service last week showed the
OL,16,Fcountry's prison population had
OL,17,Freached a record high of 8,430.
OL,19,FThere were 196 inmates at HMP
OL,20,FDumfries, which is more than 10% above
OL,21,Fthe capacity of 176.
