OL,3,COvercrowded and understaffed -
OL,4,CScottish prisons pushed to "crisis
OL,5,Cpoint"
OL,7,FThe Scottish Government wants to free
OL,8,Fanother 1,000, in plans approved by
OL,9,FHolyrood's Criminal Justice Committee.
OL,11,FSpeaking about the situation the
OL,12,FJustice Secretary, Angela Constance,
OL,13,Fsaid: "It's an emergency situation
OL,14,Fbecause of the risk to the health,
OL,15,Fwellbeing and safety of both staff and
OL,16,Fprisoners.
OL,18,F"So doing nothing is not an option."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
