OL,3,COvercrowded and understaffed -
OL,4,CScottish prisons pushed to "crisis
OL,5,Cpoint"
OL,7,FHowever, MSPs still have to vote on
OL,8,Fthese proposals before they are given
OL,9,Fthe go ahead.
OL,11,FThe Chief Inspector of Prisons for
OL,12,FScotland told ITV Border she agreed
OL,13,Fwith the union's assessment that the
OL,14,Fprison service was at "crisis point".
OL,16,FWhile releasing prisoners early could
OL,17,Fhelp in the short term, there are
OL,18,Fconcerns that longer term fixes will
OL,19,Fbe needed to tackle the wider issues.
